sentences: Kalitha Dorothy Fox (1894 – 11 August 1934) was an English composer and author.
Little is known about her, except that she had a viola sonata broadcast from Bournemouth.
Chamber musicScherzo in C for violin and piano, Op.
Chant élégiaque for cello and piano, Op.
Sonata in C minor for viola and piano, Op.
On the Death of My Mother (published 1906); arrangement by L. L.
